channel.title: God-Scape PvP V3.5 Server and Client!
channel.description:
Hey guys this is my first server so please tell me how i did :)
Credits- -40% to crazy pvp cammy edition base -40% to me for coding this -20% to tuts on mopar for helping me
~Features~ -Cool custom items like zaros god-sword,Guthix god-sword, energy sword and more! -Working pk point system -D claws hit 4X -Staff items including Staff Capes -Donator items including Donator Cape and Shield -Staff Zone -Donator zone -Working yell channel [::message] -Real God-Sword Stances like in rs -Skillcapes -In-Game top 5 Pker list -Working Veng,Energy transfer and Heal other. -Astral runes look like astrals and not skulls. -And many more that I haven't listed or are in progress! -Sweet home! -Portals to get in and out of pvp
~Commands for players~ -::players -::Info -::pickup -::master -::pure -::train -::message
Pics-These are old pics i made 4 putting on server status pages. I guess they will do until i make new ones for this.[img]http://img26.imageshack.us/img26/8779/35389909.gif[/img]
Server download-[url=http://uppit.com/v/JGL3GJLQ]http://uppit.com/v/JGL3GJLQ[/url]
Client download-[url=http://uppit.com/v/1JGLSVPM]http://uppit.com/v/1JGLSVPM[/url]
